    "description": "<p>For the duration, you deal +1 Umbral damage on Martial Attacks.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Spell Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><p><strong>Damage: (2 MP, Repeatable)</strong> Your Attacks affected by this Spell deal +1 Umbral damage.</p><p><strong>Effortless: (1 MP)</strong> You no longer need to Sustain the Spell.</p><p><strong>Dooming Strikes: (X MP)</strong> Once per round, 1 target of an Attack affected by this Spell makes a Charisma Save against your Save DC. <strong>Save Failure:</strong> The target is Doomed X for 1 round.</p><p><strong>Draining Strikes: (X MP)</strong> Once per attack, when you deal damage to a target with an Attack affected by this Spell, you can spend up to X Rest Points, regaining HP equal to the Rest Points Spent.</p>",
